## Goto mode (prefix: g)
Go to line number <n> else start of file|g
Go to end of file|e
Go to files in the selection|f
Go to start of line|h
Go to end of line|l
Go to first non-whitespace character of line|s
Go to top of screen|t
Go to middle of screen|c
Go to bottom of screen|b
Go to definition (LSP)|d
Go to type definition (LSP)|y
Go to references (LSP)|r
Go to implementation (LSP)|i
Go to last accessed/alternate file|a
Go to last modified/alternate file|m
Go to next buffer|n
Go to previous buffer|p
Go to last modification in current file|.
Move down textual (instead of visual) line|j
Move up textual (instead of visual) line|k
